The â€˜Schoolsâ€™ section gives access to the database (see <a href="http://www.poms.ac.uk/schools/interactive-labs/" target="_blank">interactive labs</a>) and other information from the research projects that created the database (see <a href="http://www.poms.ac.uk/schools/wars-of-independence/" target="_blank">Wars of Independence</a>) that is directly relevant for schools.

