<h3>Ten or more co-witnessing instances</h3>
What this means is that we have taken the sociogram of all witnesses to charters, charter/brieves, notifications, agreements and settlements in the PoMS database, up to 1286, and filtered them to show only those people who witnessed alongside each other (co-witnessed) more ten or more times. This is the resulting <a href="http://db.poms.ac.uk/sna/all/39/" target="_blank">Gephi visualization</a>.
